results.name: Sum of odd divisors of n that are < sqrt(n).
mathematica: nmax = 90; CoefficientList[Series[Sum[(2 k - 1) x^(2 k (2 k - 1))/(1 - x^(2 k - 1)), {k, 1, nmax}], {x, 0, nmax}], x] // Rest
